	CDN buckets:

		- d33lglhhb8q63m.cloudfront.net
		- d3ict7m6m7fhlt.cloudfront.net | s3.amazonaws.com/widgets.sodahead.com/
		- d6fekxp9qbg3b.cloudfront.net


	Problematic subdomains:

		- images *
		- statics *
		- widgets *

